<figureCitation box="[168,288,491,515]" captionStart="Figure 19" captionStartId="34.[168,231,1854,1874]" captionTargetBox="[168,1420,160,1829]" captionTargetId="figure-43@34.[168,1420,160,1829]" captionTargetPageId="34" captionText="Figure 19. POACEAE A. Mesosetum ferrugineum. B. Panicum rudgei. C. P. sellowii. D. Paspalum erianthum. E. P. eucomum. F. P. filifolium. G. P. pectinatum. H. P. polyphyllum." pageId="28" pageNumber="535">Figure 19B</figureCitation>
